---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---

<MainLayout title="Privacy Policy" description="Privacy Policy and Personal Data Protection of SAS AVIACO FRANCE">
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="relative text-white py-20 md:py-28 lg:py-32 overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 -z-10">
      <img 
        src="/copter/3.jpg" 
        alt="Helicopter" 
        class="w-full h-full object-cover"
        loading="eager"
      />
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-black/60 via-black/50 to-black/60"></div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 relative z-10">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
        <h1 class="font-outfit font-bold text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl mb-4">
          Privacy Policy
        </h1>
        <p class="font-outfit text-xl md:text-2xl text-gray-100">
          Protection of Your Personal Data
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Content Section -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-20">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto prose prose-lg dark:prose-invert">
        <div class="space-y-8">
          <div>
            <p class="font-outfit text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
              <strong>Last updated :</strong> {new Date().toLocaleDateString('en-US', { year: 'numeric', month: 'long', day: 'numeric' })}
            </p>
            <p class="font-outfit text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mt-4">
              SAS AVIACO FRANCE ("we", "our", "us") is committed to protecting and respecting your privacy. This privacy policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and protect your personal information when you use our website.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="font-outfit font-bold text-2xl md:text-3xl mb-4 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
              1. Data Controller
            </h2>
            <div class="font-outfit text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed space-y-2">
              <p><strong>Company Name :</strong> SAS AVIACO FRANCE</p>
              <p><strong>Registered Office :</strong> Marignane, France</p>
              <p><strong>Email :</strong> <a href="mailto:contact@aviaco.fr" class="text-primary hover:underline">contact@aviaco.fr</a></p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="font-outfit font-bold text-2xl md:text-3xl mb-4 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
              2. Data Collected
            </h2>
            <p class="font-outfit text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">
              We collect the following types of personal data :
            </p>
            <ul class="font-outfit text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed space-y-2 list-disc list-inside ml-4">
              <li><strong>Identification Data :</strong> name, first name, email address, phone number</li>
              <li><strong>Connection Data :</strong> IP address, login credentials, passwords (hashed)</li>
              <li><strong>Transaction Data :</strong> order history, payment information</li>
              <li><strong>Navigation Data :</strong> cookies, browsing data, preferences</li>
              <li><strong>Location Data :</strong> postal address for delivery</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="font-outfit font-bold text-2xl md:text-3xl mb-4 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
              3. Processing Purposes
            </h2>
            <p class="font-outfit text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">
              Your personal data is processed for the following purposes :
            </p>
            <ul class="font-outfit text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed space-y-2 list-disc list-inside ml-4">
              <li>Management of your user account</li>
              <li>Processing and tracking of your orders</li>
              <li>Customer relationship management and support</li>
              <li>Improvement of our services and user experience</li>
              <li>Sending commercial information (with your consent)</li>
              <li>Compliance with our legal and regulatory obligations</li>
              <li>Fraud prevention and website security</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="font-outfit font-bold text-2xl md:text-3xl mb-4 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
              4. Legal Basis for Processing
            </h2>
            <p class="font-outfit text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
              The processing of your personal data is based on :
            </p>
            <ul class="font-outfit text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed space-y-2 list-disc list-inside ml-4 mt-4">
              <li>Performance of a contract or pre-contractual measures</li>
              <li>Your consent for marketing communications</li>
              <li>Compliance with legal obligations</li>
              <li>Our legitimate interest in improving our services</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="font-outfit font-bold text-2xl md:text-3xl mb-4 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
              5. Data Retention
            </h2>
            <p class="font-outfit text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
              We retain your personal data only for the duration necessary for the purposes for which they were collected :
            </p>
            <ul class="font-outfit text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed space-y-2 list-disc list-inside ml-4 mt-4">
              <li>Account data : account lifetime + 3 years after closure</li>
              <li>Order data : 10 years (legal accounting obligation)</li>
              <li>Prospecting data : 3 years from last contact</li>
              <li>Cookies : maximum 13 months</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="font-outfit font-bold text-2xl md:text-3xl mb-4 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
              6. Data Sharing
            </h2>
            <p class="font-outfit text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
              Your personal data may be shared with :
            </p>
            <ul class="font-outfit text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed space-y-2 list-disc list-inside ml-4 mt-4">
              <li>Our technical service providers (hosting, payment, delivery)</li>
              <li>Our business partners (only with your consent)</li>
              <li>Competent authorities in case of legal obligation</li>
            </ul>
            <p class="font-outfit text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mt-4">
              We never sell your personal data to third parties.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="font-outfit font-bold text-2xl md:text-3xl mb-4 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
              7. Your Rights
            </h2>
            <p class="font-outfit text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">
              In accordance with the GDPR, you have the following rights :
            </p>
            <ul class="font-outfit text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed space-y-2 list-disc list-inside ml-4">
              <li><strong>Right of Access :</strong> obtain a copy of your personal data</li>
              <li><strong>Right of Rectification :</strong> correct your inaccurate or incomplete data</li>
              <li><strong>Right to Erasure :</strong> delete your data in certain cases</li>
              <li><strong>Right to Restriction :</strong> limit the processing of your data</li>
              <li><strong>Right to Data Portability :</strong> retrieve your data in a structured format</li>
              <li><strong>Right to Object :</strong> object to the processing of your data</li>
              <li><strong>Right to Withdraw Consent :</strong> at any time for processing based on consent</li>
            </ul>
            <p class="font-outfit text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mt-4">
              To exercise these rights, contact us at : <a href="mailto:contact@aviaco.fr" class="text-primary hover:underline">contact@aviaco.fr</a>
            </p>
            <p class="font-outfit text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mt-4">
              You also have the right to lodge a complaint with the CNIL (Commission Nationale de l'Informatique et des Libert√©s) if you believe that the processing of your data constitutes a violation of the GDPR.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="font-outfit font-bold text-2xl md:text-3xl mb-4 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
              8. Cookies
            </h2>
            <p class="font-outfit text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
              Our website uses cookies to improve your browsing experience. Cookies are small text files stored on your device. We use technical cookies necessary for the website's operation and analytical cookies to understand how you use our website.
            </p>
            <p class="font-outfit text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mt-4">
              You can manage your cookie preferences in your browser settings. However, disabling certain cookies may affect the website's functionality.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="font-outfit font-bold text-2xl md:text-3xl mb-4 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
              9. Security
            </h2>
            <p class="font-outfit text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
              We implement appropriate technical and organizational measures to protect your personal data against any unauthorized access, loss, destruction, or alteration. However, no method of transmission over the Internet or electronic storage is completely secure.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="font-outfit font-bold text-2xl md:text-3xl mb-4 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
              10. International Transfers
            </h2>
            <p class="font-outfit text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
              Your data may be transferred and stored in countries located outside the European Union. In this case, we ensure that appropriate safeguards are in place to protect your data in accordance with the GDPR.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="font-outfit font-bold text-2xl md:text-3xl mb-4 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
              11. Modifications
            </h2>
            <p class="font-outfit text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
              We may modify this privacy policy at any time. Changes will be published on this page with an indication of the last update date. We encourage you to consult this page regularly to stay informed about how we protect your data.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="font-outfit font-bold text-2xl md:text-3xl mb-4 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
              12. Contact
            </h2>
            <p class="font-outfit text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
              For any questions regarding this privacy policy or to exercise your rights, you can contact us at :
            </p>
            <div class="font-outfit text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mt-4 space-y-2">
              <p><strong>Email :</strong> <a href="mailto:contact@aviaco.fr" class="text-primary hover:underline">contact@aviaco.fr</a></p>
              <p><strong>Company :</strong> SAS AVIACO FRANCE</p>
              <p><strong>Address :</strong> Marignane, France</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</MainLayout>

